highlights.text: “Deslocado” by NAPA has been on Viral Songs Global the longest, at 72 days straight.
“Sabbath Bloody Sabbath - 2014 Remaster” by Black Sabbath is the highest new entry on Viral Songs Global at #92.
Ozzy Osbourne has the most spots on Viral Songs Global. “Mama, I'm Coming Home” is the highest at #1.
“Oneida” by Tyler Childers is the biggest gainer on Viral Songs Global, up 15 spots at #81.
